|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[l_orderkey@4 as l_orderkey, o_orderdate@0 as o_orderdate, o_shippriority@1 as o_shippriority], aggr=[sum(lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - lineitem.l_discount)]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
