|               |                 HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(o_orderkey@1, l_orderkey@2)], projection=[o_orderdate@0, o_shippriority@2, l_discount@3, l_extendedprice@4, l_orderkey@5]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
